title: Basil Rathbone Reads Edgar Allan Poe
description:
Edgar Allen Poe, Poems and Tales, Vol.1 - Caedmon TC 1028 (Basil Rathbone reads The Raven, Annabel Lee, Eldorado, To -- --, The Masque of the Red Death, Alone, The City in the Sea, The Black Cat.)

Edgar Allen Poe, Vol. 2 - Caedmon TC 1115 (Basil Rathbone reads The Cask of Amontillado, The Facts in the Case of M. Valdemar, The Pit and the Pendulum.)

Edgar Allen Poe, Vol 3 - Caedmon TC 1195 (Basil Rathbone reads The Telltale Heart, The Fall of the House of Usher, The Bells, The Haunted)
